On  Sat, 28 Feb 1998 Eugene Leitl <eugene@liposome.genebee.msu.su> Wrote:

        >Unless you are a massive, unstructured superalloy sphere you won't         
        >survive a nuke fireball from a few m distance virtually unscathed. 
          

